 if(!flag)printf(&amp;#34;0.000000000000\n&amp;#34;);
 return 0;
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;想不通，没办法只好换思路。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The equation-SGU106（扩展欧几里得）</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/euclid/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Aug 2018 10:32:39 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/euclid/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="题意"&gt;&lt;span&gt;10 题意&lt;/span&gt;
